node.text: I have always wanted try @sarahsloft cake but didn’t because they are not gluten free and unsuitable for my elder boys. So when I saw their #stayhome dessert box, you can imagine how happy I was! Even more pleased with the food! Again, look and taste equally amazing. 👍🏻
@msclak yes dear. I am a sucker for beautiful 🍰! 😊
@rinyks thank you lovely!! ❤️ I really enjoyed them.
@pandavaleris I must be super lucky then! 💕 Hope they can continue with box like this so  get to try different flavors instead of 1 whole cake which is too large for me. 😂
Wanted to get it too but they were sold out
@turquoise__sky yes hun and taste amazing too! 😋
@little_camillatayjx indeed dear! They are super pretty! 💕✨
